    {
      "title": "Find the original median",
      "content": "The original set 6, 6, 8, 8, 8, 10, 21 has 7 values. The median is the 4th value: <strong>8</strong>."
    },
    {
      "title": "Find which choice has median 8",
      "content": "Each choice has 6 values; its median = average of 3rd and 4th values."
    },
    {
      "title": "Evaluate all choices",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>$4$, $6$, $6$, $6$, $8$, $8$</strong> $4$, $6$, $6$, $6$, $8$, $8$ — median = (6+6)/2 = 6. Eliminated.</li><li><strong>$6$, $6$, $8$, $8$, $10$, $10$</strong> $6$, $6$, $8$, $8$, $10$, $10$ — median = (8+8)/2 = 8. That is the correct answer.</li><li><strong>$6$, $8$, $10$, $10$, $10$, $12$</strong> $6$, $8$, $10$, $10$, $10$, $12$ — median = (10+10)/2 = 10. Eliminated.</li><li><strong>$8$, $8$, $10$, $10$, $21$, $21$</strong> $8$, $8$, $10$, $10$, $21$, $21$ — median = (10+10)/2 = 10. Eliminated.</li></ul>"
